[SKYJO](https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgame/204135/skyjo) is a card game.  

This repo exposes an API to play SKYJO using a simplified bare-bone JSON interface linking different game actions to
end-points via Flask. 

## Requirements ##
`Poetry` for package management.
See `pyproject.toml`.

## Setup ##
`make setup`

## Playing the game ##
Run `flask run` on the project root directory.
Connect to `http://127.0.0.1:5000` on your browser.
